to run a test instance "./devserve" or:

  go run serve.go -postpath docs

to build:

  go build serve.go

to run my prod instance:

  cd /homedisk/$USER/.d
  blog/bindcap blog/serve \
    -acmepath ~/.d/certbot \
    -certpath certbot/live/notech.ie \
    -dnsurl "$(cat ~/.config/dnsurl)" \
    -gopherport 70 \
    -httpport -80 \
    -httpsport 443 \
    -mondomain notech.ie \
    -postpath blog/docs \
    -redirecthttp

to regen the backup site:

  ./serve -postpath docs -dumpall >docs/index.html

to refresh the certs:

 dir=$HOME/.d/certbot
 certbot renew --config-dir=$dir --work-dir=$dir --logs-dir=$dir
